citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:10 pm on
06-Feb-18.
USDA officials arrived at the facility at 1:10 pm and spoke with the licensee over the phone who stated she was not
available for the inspection.
Additional Inspectors
Cole Heather, Supervisory Animal Care Specialist
Steneroden Katie, Veterinary Medical Officer
